  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This Avalanche is coming.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your character with 100+ cosmetics!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 10+ different zones with new obstacles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete daily challenges to get coins more quickly!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run is unique with pseudo-random map generation!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control Options:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow Keys</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FlurryHurry is now available on PC!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mobile Ads are disabled for the PC version.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support is disabled as it negated most of the game's challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily Challenges are given a multiplier to make up for the removal of Optional Ads.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This Avalanche is coming.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your character with 100+ cosmetics!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 10+ different zones with new obstacles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete daily challenges to get coins more quickly!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run is unique with pseudo-random map generation!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control Options:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow Keys</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FlurryHurry is now available on PC!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mobile Ads are disabled for the PC version.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support is disabled as it negated most of the game's challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily Challenges are given a multiplier to make up for the removal of Optional Ads.</p></li></ul>",
